Spin a new lxc. Then follow:

sed -i 's/# deb-src /deb-src /g' /etc/apt/sources.list
sudo apt update
sudo apt install ubuntu-dev-tools devscripts
pull-lp-source PACKAGE focal
cd PACKAGE-VERSION
sudo apt build-dep PACKAGE
dch # make changes
debuild -S 
(or build without signing: debuild -i -us -uc -S)
## Then get ouft of lxc; signing from inside "su - user" doesn't work.
debsign -k pponnuvel@gmail.com PACKAGE_5.0-6ubuntu1_source.changes
Create a ppa from the launchpad
Upload with: dput ppa:pponnuvel/PACKAGE-5.0 PACKAGE_5.0-6ubuntu1_source.changes


Docs:
https://manpages.debian.org/stretch/devscripts/debuild.1.en.html
https://help.launchpad.net/Packaging

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zQo6hPfl5iM
https://docs.ceph.com/docs/master/install/build-ceph/
https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SimpleSbuild
https://packaging.ubuntu.com/html/setting-up-sbuild.html


#######
Get specific source e.g. pull-uca-source ceph 14.2.1-0ubuntu1
